reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt White Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: I purchased two of these bands to go on either side of my wedding ring. Each band was very sparkly and I was quite pleased. The quality of workmanship was on par with what I've seen in jewelry stores. I ended up returning the rings because they made my ring too wide for my finger, but the rings were beautiful with no issues.
reviews.title: Beautiful, thin, sparkly band

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt White Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: I got this for a wedding band. It's very tiny and pretty just as I wanted. Diamonds are prong set which went great with my wedding band. Only complaint is when the band moved around the tiny diamonds and studs rub adjoining fingers. I'm sure I will get used to it the more I wear it.
reviews.title: Tiny and pretty!

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt White Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: Its worth the price...although the diamonds were small but they are really noticeable because they are sparkling and twinkling like a star.
reviews.title: nice ring with sparkling diamonds...

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt White Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: Bought as a wedding ring... absolutely love the way it complements the engagment ring without over powering it.
reviews.title: complements well to my engagment ring!

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt White Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this ring, it looks so nice with my princess cut solitaire. It was a little thinner than I expected, but still overall gorgeous.
reviews.title: Beautiful ring
